{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":800,"text":"I've been doing some thinking."},{"time":4240,"text":"I'm going to kill my dad."},{"time":7200,"text":"I called my sister."}]},{"cues":[{"time":8440,"text":"\"Listen,"},{"time":9960,"text":"I've been doing some thinking."},{"time":12480,"text":"I'm going to kill Dad."},{"time":15480,"text":"I'm going to take him to Oregon,"},{"time":18080,"text":"find some heroin,"},{"time":20000,"text":"and give it to him.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":22720,"text":"My dad has frontotemporal lobe dementia,"},{"time":24880,"text":"or FTD."},{"time":26640,"text":"It's a confusing disease\nthat hits people in their 50s or 60s."},{"time":29600,"text":"It can completely change\nsomeone's personality,"},{"time":32520,"text":"making them paranoid and even violent."},{"time":35400,"text":"My dad's been sick for a decade,"},{"time":37360,"text":"but three years ago he got really sick,"},{"time":39920,"text":"and we had to move him out of his house --"},{"time":42280,"text":"the house that I grew up in,"},{"time":44240,"text":"the house that he built\nwith his own hands."},{"time":47160,"text":"My strapping, cool dad\nwith the falsetto singing voice"},{"time":52400,"text":"had to move into a facility\nfor round-the-clock care"},{"time":54853,"text":"when he was just 65."}]},{"cues":[{"time":58960,"text":"At first my mom and sisters\nand I made the mistake"},{"time":61640,"text":"of putting him in a regular nursing home."},{"time":64599,"text":"It was really pretty;"},{"time":65880,"text":"it had plush carpet\nand afternoon art classes"},{"time":68840,"text":"and a dog named Diane."},{"time":71520,"text":"But then I got a phone call."}]},{"cues":[{"time":74520,"text":"\"Ms. Malone, we've arrested your father.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":78800,"text":"\"What?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":80760,"text":"\"Well, he threatened\neverybody with cutlery."},{"time":84960,"text":"And then he yanked\nthe curtains off the wall,"},{"time":87120,"text":"and then he tried\nto throw plants out the window."},{"time":90280,"text":"And then, well, he pulled all\nthe old ladies out of their wheelchairs.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":97200,"text":"\"All the old ladies?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":98600,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":99800,"text":"\"What a cowboy.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":101080,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":102760,"text":"After he got kicked out of there,"},{"time":104400,"text":"we bounced him between\na bunch of state-run facilities"},{"time":107000,"text":"before finding a treatment center\nspecifically for people with dementia."},{"time":111280,"text":"At first, he kind of liked it,"},{"time":113360,"text":"but over time his health declined,"},{"time":115320,"text":"and one day I walked in"},{"time":116600,"text":"and found him sitting hunched over\non the ground wearing a onesie --"},{"time":120840,"text":"those kinds of outfits\nthat zip in the back."},{"time":125760,"text":"I watched him for about an hour\nas he yanked at it,"},{"time":129000,"text":"trying to find a way out of this thing."},{"time":132000,"text":"And it's supposed to be practical,"},{"time":134880,"text":"but to me it looked like a straightjacket."},{"time":137760,"text":"And so I ran out."},{"time":140520,"text":"I left him there."},{"time":143440,"text":"I sat in my truck -- his old truck --"},{"time":145720,"text":"hunched over,"},{"time":147360,"text":"this really deep guttural cry\ncoming out of the pit of my belly."},{"time":151480,"text":"I just couldn't believe that my father,"},{"time":155880,"text":"the Adonis of my youth,"},{"time":158960,"text":"my really dear friend,"},{"time":161640,"text":"would think that this kind of life\nwas worth living anymore."}]},{"cues":[{"time":166520,"text":"We're programmed\nto prioritize productivity."},{"time":170720,"text":"So when a person --\nan Adonis in this case --"},{"time":174080,"text":"is no longer productive\nin the way we expect him to be,"},{"time":177760,"text":"the way that he expects himself to be,"},{"time":180600,"text":"what value does that life have left?"},{"time":183640,"text":"That day in the truck,"},{"time":185520,"text":"all I could imagine\nwas that my dad was being tortured"},{"time":189720,"text":"and his body was\nthe vessel of that torture."},{"time":194040,"text":"I've got to get him out of that body."},{"time":196600,"text":"I've got to get him out of that body;\nI'm going to kill Dad."}]},{"cues":[{"time":200600,"text":"I call my sister."}]},{"cues":[{"time":203400,"text":"\"Beth,\" she said."},{"time":208800,"text":"\"You don't want\nto live the rest of your life"},{"time":210960,"text":"knowing that you killed your father."},{"time":212800,"text":"And you'd be arrested I think,"},{"time":214920,"text":"because he can't condone it."},{"time":216520,"text":"And you don't even know\nhow to buy heroin.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":218800,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":219840,"text":"It's true, I don't."}]},{"cues":[{"time":221120,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":224200,"text":"The truth is we talk\nabout his death a lot."},{"time":226280,"text":"When will it happen? What will it be like?"},{"time":228304,"text":"But I wish that we would have talked\nabout death when we were all healthy."},{"time":232400,"text":"What does my best death look like?"},{"time":235880,"text":"What does your best death look like?"},{"time":238840,"text":"But my family didn't know to do that."},{"time":241680,"text":"And my sister was right."},{"time":243800,"text":"I shouldn't murder Dad with heroin,"},{"time":246800,"text":"but I've got to get him out of that body."}]},{"cues":[{"time":250560,"text":"So I went to a psychic."},{"time":252760,"text":"And then a priest,\nand then a support group,"},{"time":254880,"text":"and they all said the same thing:"},{"time":256519,"text":"sometimes people hang on\nwhen they're worried about loved ones."},{"time":259640,"text":"Just tell them you're safe,\nand it's OK to go when you're ready."}]},{"cues":[{"time":263600,"text":"So I went to see Dad."},{"time":265840,"text":"I found him hunched over\non the ground in the onesie."},{"time":268360,"text":"He was staring past me\nand just kind of looking at the ground."},{"time":271400,"text":"I gave him a ginger ale"},{"time":272680,"text":"and just started talking\nabout nothing in particular,"},{"time":275320,"text":"but as I was talking,\nhe sneezed from the ginger ale."},{"time":280000,"text":"And the sneeze --\nit jerked his body upright,"},{"time":283640,"text":"sparking him back to life a little bit."},{"time":285600,"text":"And he just kept drinking and sneezing\nand sparking, over and over and over again"},{"time":290800,"text":"until it stopped."},{"time":293280,"text":"And I heard,"},{"time":295440,"text":"\"Heheheheheh,"},{"time":297320,"text":"heheheheheh ..."},{"time":300080,"text":"this is so fabulous."},{"time":303760,"text":"This is so fabulous.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":306480,"text":"His eyes were open\nand he was looking at me,"},{"time":309320,"text":"and I said, \"Hi, Dad!\""},{"time":311200,"text":"and he said, \"Hiya, Beth.\""},{"time":315480,"text":"And I opened my mouth to tell him, right?"},{"time":317480,"text":"\"Dad, if you want to die, you can die."},{"time":320080,"text":"We're all OK.\""},{"time":321960,"text":"But as I opened my mouth to tell him,"},{"time":323800,"text":"all I could say was, \"Dad!"},{"time":328160,"text":"I miss you.\""},{"time":330160,"text":"And then he said, \"Well, I miss you, too.\""},{"time":332920,"text":"And then I just fell over\nbecause I'm just a mess."}]},{"cues":[{"time":335640,"text":"So I fell over and I sat there with him"},{"time":340680,"text":"because for the first time in a long time\nhe seemed kind of OK."},{"time":344840,"text":"And I memorized his hands,"},{"time":347520,"text":"feeling so grateful that his spirit\nwas still attached to his body."},{"time":353400,"text":"And in that moment I realized"},{"time":356120,"text":"I'm not responsible for this person."},{"time":359560,"text":"I'm not his doctor,"},{"time":361080,"text":"I'm not his mother,"},{"time":363160,"text":"I'm certainly not his God,"},{"time":365520,"text":"and maybe the best way to help him and me"},{"time":369280,"text":"is to resume our roles\nas father and daughter."}]},{"cues":[{"time":373360,"text":"And so we just sat there,"},{"time":375440,"text":"calm and quiet like we've always done."},{"time":378040,"text":"Nobody was productive."},{"time":380800,"text":"Both of us are still strong."}]},{"cues":[{"time":385240,"text":"\"OK, Dad. I'm going to go,"},{"time":388320,"text":"but I'll see you tomorrow.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":391360,"text":"\"OK,\" he said."},{"time":394880,"text":"\"Hey,"},{"time":396920,"text":"this is a pretty nice hacienda.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":399960,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":401200,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}